      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, making it a reliable choice for a daily driver. While the exterior looks great, you will find some minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with normal use. Inside, the cabin is clean and all electronics are fully functional, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. It is a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner.",
