    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's looking for a new home! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is in really solid shape. I've taken great care of it, and it drives like a dream. Perfect for someone looking for a dependable car without the 'new car' price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love it! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
