      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and ready for its next adventure. I've made sure to keep up with the basics so you can just hop in and go. Honestly, it\u2019s a fantastic find for anyone looking for a dependable car that still looks sharp on the road. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
