    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six. This unit features a 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The Double VANOS system has been overhauled for optimal variable valve timing. While the aesthetics reflect its 'good' condition status with minor wear, the powertrain and suspension geometry remain precise, offering the visceral, high-RPM engagement characteristic of this chassis. Ready for spirited canyon carving or track-day duty.",
